separately under NVIDIA Open Model Development and Weight License 1.1
(OpenMDW 1.1). Any derived model artifact must preserve the applicable license,
attribution, use restrictions, and disclosure obligations.

NVIDIA NeMo is an external Apache-2.0 dependency. When source derived from NeMo
is copied or modified, its original copyright and license header must be kept,
and the source path and revision must be recorded.

Piper TTS is an external GPL-3.0-or-later executable dependency and is not
included in this repository. The selected initial Slovenian voice is
`sl_SI-artur-medium` from `rhasspy/piper-voices`. Its repository metadata,
model card, and ARTUR source record use inconsistent license labels; this
project applies the conservative ARTUR CC BY-SA 4.0 attribution and publication
policy until later legal review. Generated synthetic audio is not Apache-2.0
merely because the orchestration code is Apache-2.0.

